name: Pojak
description: Pojak is a revolutionary utility token designed to animate the world of memecoins and create engaging short-form content. Our innovative platform, serves as the hub for this content, featuring live content that can be broadcasted on X. We also produce and distribute snippets across social media, creating a dynamic content machine. Our development team has a proven track record, having previously launched a music platform. With Pojak, we are aiming even higher, currently boasting a market cap of $700 million. Join us as we redefine the intersection of cryptocurrency and digital entertainment.
